Pubg Pro, Batti God, Goldie boi, kaisa chaap lete ho itna, bhai kuch bhee aur kaisi bhee situation ho tujhe bas haste hue hee dekha hai. 2 saal full magai aur baaki 2 saal full on anime aur TV series. 

Winter break mujhe hamesha yaad rahega...bhai kya epic reason diya tha campus me rukne ka.....Kaafi masti kari thee humne saath me.

Ab to bhai GS jaa raha hai....GF milte hee apne wingies ko bhool mat jana...All the best bro..!!
author: Kushagra Gupta (R Gupta)
